# üì¶ Installation
Currently, we use this package internally on our [Monorepo](https://github.com/BrokenSource/BrokenSource)

- Until we publish this package to **PyPI**, you can install it from **GitHub**:

```bash
pip install git+https://github.com/BrokenSource/BrokenEnum.git
```

